snippet.title: Ninja Niko tricks the Deer in 99 NiGHTS on Roblox!!
snippet.description:
JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/@GforGaming

HEY EVERYBODY!! 

We have another CRAZY moment from our G for Gaming video where Adley, Niko, Navey, Dad and Ethan from Spacestation Apps played 99 Nights in the Forest on Roblox and got super far into the game! We were being attacked by the Deer and the cultists and Niko was the last one alive but was escaping the deer by jumping up on the walls and getting away from it until it got up to him and he started running away screaming "I'm sorry Mr. Deer"

enjoy some A for Adley videos: https://www.youtube.com/c/AforAdleyLe...
have a blast with our A for Adley Shorts: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMHpfyAqrjrhn-mRS2bUL0g
share a best day ever with our family: https://www.youtube.com/user/Shonduras
fun best day ever shorts: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgVE...
